snippet.title: Path of the Warrior Launch Trailer (Oculus Quest)
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE for More DualShockers Videos! ► http://bit.ly/2C8ipVh

Classic brawler fans who’ve migrated to VR have a new title to get excited for: Path of the Warrior., Aa classic Streets of Rage-style beat-em-up reimagined for the Oculus Quest and Oculus Rift, it releases today from developer Twisted Pixel and Oculus Studios.

VISIT US at DualShockers ►► http://bit.ly/2XEUeH5

JOIN us on DISCORD ►► http://bit.ly/2H1zBjf
